{
  "title": "ISic002997. I.Sicily inscription 002997",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>ἐπὶ ὑπάτων <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Γαΐου · Κεστί\n                    ου Μάρκου Σερουιλίου Νω\n                    νιανοῦ\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"praenomen\" data-text=\"Γαΐου\">Γ(αΐου)</span> · <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κεστί\n                    ου\">Κεστί-<br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>ου</span>  <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Μάρκου Σερουιλίου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"praenomen\" data-text=\"Μάρκου\">Μ(άρκου)</span>  <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"nomen\" data-text=\"Σερουιλίου\">Σερουιλίου</span></span>  <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"cognomen\" data-text=\"Νω\n                    νιανοῦ\">Νω-<br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>νιανοῦ</span></span> · ἀμφιπόλου δὲ <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>ἐν Συρακούσαις · <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Αὔλου · Βαλερί\n                    ου Ἀραβικοῦ\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"praenomen\" data-text=\"Αὔλου\">Α(ὔλου)</span> · <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"nomen\" data-text=\"Βαλερί\n                    ου\">Βαλερί-<br id=\"al5-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>ου</span>  <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"cognomen\" data-text=\"Ἀραβικοῦ\">Ἀραβικοῦ</span></span> τᾶν δὲ <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Παί\n                    δων\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Παί\n                    δων\">Παί-<br id=\"al6-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>δων</span></span> · <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Λουκίου · Βηβηίου Κλάδου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"praenomen\" data-text=\"Λουκίου\">Λ(ουκίου)</span> · <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"nomen\" data-text=\"Βηβηίου\">Βηβηίου</span>  <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"cognomen\" data-text=\"Κλάδου\">Κλάδου</span></span>  <br id=\"al7-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">7</span>ἱερείας δὲ <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κλωδίας Πώλ\n                    λας\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"nomen\" data-text=\"Κλωδίας\">Κλωδίας</span>  <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"cognomen\" data-text=\"Πώλ\n                    λας\">Πώλ-<br id=\"al8-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">8</span>λας</span></span> μηνὸς Πανάμου-<br id=\"al9-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">9</span>ϛκ´ παρεγένοντο πρὸς <br id=\"al10-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">10</span>τὰς <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Παῖδας\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Παῖδας\">Παῖδας</span></span> μετὰ <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Αὐλίας\n                    Τίτου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"nomen\" data-text=\"Αὐλίας\">Αὐλί[ας]</span>  <br id=\"al11-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">11</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Τίτου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Τίτου\">Τίτου</span></span></span> θυγατέρ[ος] <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Φαβία\n                    Σφονγέος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Φαβία\">Φαβία</span>  <br id=\"al12-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">12</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Σφονγέος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"filial\" data-text=\"Σφονγέος\">Σφονγέος</span></span></span> ἡ μήτη[ρ] καὶ <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Φάβιλ\n                    λα\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Φάβιλ\n                    λα\">Φ[άβιλ-]<br id=\"al13-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">13</span>λα</span></span> θυγάτηρ καὶ <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἀπία\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀπία\">Ἀπία</span></span> [τῇ] <br id=\"al14-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">14</span>τριακάδι εὐφρανθ[έντες] <br id=\"al15-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">15</span>καὶ εὐχαριστοῦ&lt;ν&gt;τες <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ἀπόλ\n                    λωνι\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀπόλ\n                    λωνι\">Ἀ[πόλ-]<br id=\"al16-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">16</span>λωνι</span></span> καὶ <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Παίδεσσι\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Παίδεσσι\">Παίδε[σσι]</span></span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>ΕΠΙΥΠΑΤΩΝ<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Γαΐου · Κεστί\n                    ου Μάρκου Σερουιλίου Νω\n                    νιανοῦ\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"praenomen\" data-text=\"Γαΐου\">Γ</span>·<span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κεστί\n                    ου\">ΚΕΣΤΙ<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>ΟΥ</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Μάρκου Σερουιλίου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"praenomen\" data-text=\"Μάρκου\">Μ</span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"nomen\" data-text=\"Σερουιλίου\">ΣΕΡΟΥΙΛΙΟΥ</span></span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"cognomen\" data-text=\"Νω\n                    νιανοῦ\">ΝΩ<br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>ΝΙΑΝΟΥ</span></span>·ΑΜΦΙΠΟΛΟΥΔΕ<br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>ΕΝΣΥΡΑΚΟΥΣΑΙΣ·<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Αὔλου · Βαλερί\n                    ου Ἀραβικοῦ\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"praenomen\" data-text=\"Αὔλου\">Α</span>·<span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"nomen\" data-text=\"Βαλερί\n                    ου\">ΒΑΛΕΡΙ<br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>ΟΥ</span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"cognomen\" data-text=\"Ἀραβικοῦ\">ΑΡΑΒΙΚΟΥ</span></span>ΤΑΝΔΕ<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Παί\n                    δων\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Παί\n                    δων\">ΠΑΙ<br id=\"al6-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>ΔΩΝ</span></span>·<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Λουκίου · Βηβηίου Κλάδου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"praenomen\" data-text=\"Λουκίου\">Λ</span>·<span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"nomen\" data-text=\"Βηβηίου\">ΒΗΒΗΙΟΥ</span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"cognomen\" data-text=\"Κλάδου\">ΚΛΑΔΟΥ</span></span><br id=\"al7-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">7</span>ΙΕΡΕΙΑΣΔΕ<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κλωδίας Πώλ\n                    λας\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"nomen\" data-text=\"Κλωδίας\">ΚΛΩΔΙΑΣ</span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"cognomen\" data-text=\"Πώλ\n                    λας\">ΠΩΛ<br id=\"al8-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">8</span>ΛΑΣ</span></span>ΜΗΝΟΣΠΑΝΑΜΟΥ<br id=\"al9-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">9</span>ϚΚΠΑΡΕΓΕΝΟΝΤΟΠΡΟΣ<br id=\"al10-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">10</span>ΤΑΣ<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Παῖδας\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Παῖδας\">ΠΑΙΔΑΣ</span></span>ΜΕΤΑ<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Αὐλίας\n                    Τίτου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"nomen\" data-text=\"Αὐλίας\">ΑΥΛΙ[..]</span><br id=\"al11-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">11</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Τίτου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Τίτου\">ΤΙΤΟΥ</span></span></span>ΘΥΓΑΤΕΡ[..]<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Φαβία\n                    Σφονγέος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Φαβία\">ΦΑΒΙΑ</span><br id=\"al12-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">12</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Σφονγέος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"filial\" data-text=\"Σφονγέος\">ΣΦΟΝΓΕΟΣ</span></span></span>ΗΜΗΤΗ[.]ΚΑΙ<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Φάβιλ\n                    λα\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Φάβιλ\n                    λα\">Φ[....]<br id=\"al13-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">13</span>ΛΑ</span></span>ΘΥΓΑΤΗΡΚΑΙ<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἀπία\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀπία\">ΑΠΙΑ</span></span>[..]<br id=\"al14-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">14</span>ΤΡΙΑΚΑΔΙΕΥΦΡΑΝΘ[.....]<br id=\"al15-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">15</span>ΚΑΙΕΥΧΑΡΙΣΤΟΥΤΕΣ<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ἀπόλ\n                    λωνι\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀπόλ\n                    λωνι\">Α[...]<br id=\"al16-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">16</span>ΛΩΝΙ</span></span>ΚΑΙ<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Παίδεσσι\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Παίδεσσι\">ΠΑΙΔΕ[...]</span></span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic002997_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2013-10-02\" src=\"ISic002997_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic002997.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2013-10-02\" src=\"ISic002997-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text after Manganaro 1992 with slight changes</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2> translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>  </p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 42.0833 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a></li><li> 1952.0199 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282</a></li><li> 1900.0091 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283</a></li><li> Orsi NSA 1899 458 no.3 ph <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392</a></li><li> Hoffmann 1904 5259 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000817\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptio